Ellie Fivas
Editorial Board Member
Ellie Fivas (she/her) (24Ox) is from Cleveland, Tennessee, and is majoring in political science and art history. She writes on the Wheel’s Editorial Board. When she is not writing for the Wheel, she serves as the Oxford-Atlanta Liaison for the Oxford and Emory SGAs. She also enjoys attending OxSAPA events and going on adventures with OutdoorOx. In her free time, she loves to read historical fiction, write, garden, embroider and do crossword puzzles.
